                 SBK Generations 2012
			
 The official game of the FIM Superbike World Championship is back and
 is now the most complete motorcycling simulation ever created! Play 
 through the last four seasons of the SBK world championships, including
 the brand new 2012 season to become world champion or test your skills 
 in the brand new SBK Experience mode. With SBK Generations, Milestone has 
 developed a masterpiece: the definitive motorcycle game, crammed with over
 220+ riders, 60 bike models, 140+ teams, 17 circuits and up to 16 player 
 online multi-player!
	
 Release name..........: SBK.Generations.MacOSX.ni7r0geN
 Publisher.............: Milestone
 Final Size............: 3.81 GB
 Platform..............: Mac OSX 10.9 and up
 Protection............: None
 Wrapper Rating........: Premium (Native level or better)

 			Intructions:
1. Unpack and drag to whatever folder and play.
2. As always configured full xBox360 gamepad support with 
	tattiebogle driver installed on the system.
3. Requires an ATI Radeon HD 2400 or better / NVidia 8600M or better.
   Default video configuration 1024x768, adjust to your resolution in
	options inside the game.
4. Do not change the wrapper engine or update the master wrapper, it 
	was optimized to run this game.
5. The image is ultra compressed, so be patient when dragging the .app
	to a destination folder.
